    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such pristine shape that it basically still has that new-car smell! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage and looks just as stunning as the day it was first bought. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out and come see it for yourself!",
