    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This example is mechanically pristine: the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under torque. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension maintains its original compliance with refreshed bushings and dampers, while the chassis remains free of oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
