    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly showroom-quality 2018 BMW M3 in Alpine White over Sakhir Orange Extended Merino Leather. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain, let alone snow. The exterior is flawless, featuring a professional-grade ceramic coating that yields a deep, glass-like finish; there are zero stone chips, dings, or swirl marks. The 19-inch 437M wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, retaining that factory scent. There is no bolster wear on the heated seats, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any hairline scratches. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
