      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been pampered in a garage and treated like a member of the family! There isn't a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I know I'm still building up my seller rating here, but I promise this car is the real deal and even more stunning in person. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and fall in love with it just like I did!",
